Template Scaffold Permission

PortableMC grants permission to copy and adapt only the files explicitly
located under the template scaffolding modules:

- template-common
- template-fabric-1201
- template-forge-1201
- template-fabric-1211
- template-neoforge-1211

This permission exists solely to create a standalone mod scaffold from those
template files. It does not grant rights to Portable API source code, binaries,
documentation, branding, release artifacts, package names, Maven coordinates,
or any other repository content.
